  "body": "Type: **Bug**\r\n\r\nSummary: The link is not clickable when it was sent wrapped up with asterisks (*) or tildes (~)\r\n\r\n**Expected behaviour**\r\n\r\nThe link should be clickable no matter the format\r\n\r\n**Actual behaviour**\r\n\r\nThe link is not clickable when it was sent wrapped up with asterisks (*) or tildes (~), for sender and a recipient both\r\n\r\n**Reproduction**\r\n\r\n1. Open Status\r\n2. Start 1-1 chat/public chat\r\n3. Copy a valid link and paste it, wrapped up with asterisks (*) or tildes (~)\r\n4. Try clicking on your link to open it, as a sender or a recepient\r\n\r\n**Additional Information**\r\n\r\nStatus version: Develop (d2160e)\r\nOperating System: iOS 12.0, MacOS 10.13.4",
